            <button data-close-button class="close-button">&times;</button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            Chimney Rock Trail from Headquarters is a 2.2 mile heavily trafficked out and back trail located
            near Thurmont, Maryland that offers the chance to see wildlife and is rated as moderate. The trail
             is primarily used for hiking, walking, running, and nature trips.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="overlay"></div>


<!--Button 5-->
